Packed layout record Word has value: u16.

To layout read from view, giving i32.
Let bytes be buffer of 4 u8 filled with 0.
bytes at 1 becomes 42.
bytes at 2 becomes 0.
Let window be view of bytes from 1 for 2.
Let word be read Word from window at 0.
Give word.value as i32.

To main, giving i32.
Give layout read from view.
